  "detailed_description": "<h1>My first 3D game!</h1><p></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Art by Igor Shalimov</h2><br><strong>Important information</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Press \"N\" for night mode.<br></li><li>Press \"Del\" then \"Esc\" to reset all achievements.</li></ul><br>100 hidden cups is a hidden object game in the surreal setting.<br>Black and white hand-drawn graphics. Ultra hard!<br><br>The strange cups are hidden on the paper. <br>A difficult adventure for the eyes.<br><br>Can you find 100 cups? Just click on the cup!<br>Take care of your nerves!",
